<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_f36f5add-48f8-4447-a0b6-7fa2005ebcf4" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="SA"><sptc>I4D4</sptc><title id="_789df728-3c07-4615-ac31-6d3b965cc361">Protection of openings</title><subclause id="_cb4655ec-629e-4252-8c0d-f5e6e5dd4cca" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a9ace72d-c01d-424c-bd82-8f9e99fda9af">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Where external stairs, ramps or ladders are used as an exit in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_f56b046e-2a81-496b-8214-0bc4adde14f5" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref>—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_32191d31-7911-48f2-982d-290ff82b39ba">any window or door opening within 6 m of the stairway or ladder must be protected in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1329_1.2.0.xml#_145deef2-6101-494c-89a7-a771d714af1d" id="_50f09789-4667-4e52-848d-0c8d4dce150e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">C4D5</xref>; or</li><li id="_5e70cfd6-dc94-4365-9f6c-73a898762803">the stairway, ramp or ladder must be enclosed for its full height above the lowest level of the window or door opening with non-combustible construction having an FRL of not less than 60/60/60.</li></ol></subclause></clause>